arStrings.szText: Collect {c_highlight}Proofs of Might{/c} before the timer ends. Earn {c_highlight}Proofs{/c} by slaying monsters; defeating {c_highlight}Bosses{/c} will also drop a powerful {c_highlight}Shrine{/c}.
You will also earn {c_highlight}Proofs{/c} by opening {c_highlight}locked Chests{/c}. {c_highlight}Keys{/c} will drop from a specified {c_highlight}Elite{/c} monster.
{c_highlight}Pillars{/c} are a new type of {c_highlight}Shrine{/c} that boost your {c_highlight}Score{/c} potential.
Be sure to {c_highlight}avoid dying{/c}! If you do, you will {c_highlight}drop{/c} a percentage of your {c_highlight}Proofs{/c}.
